<%= render "/shared/mailers/header" %>
<p>Dear <%= @user %>,</p>

<p><%= @reservation.owner %> has made a reservation for <%= @listing %> on <%= l(@reservation.date, :format => :long) %>.
<%- if @reservation.comment -%></p>

<p>They said:</p>

<p>"<%= @reservation.comment %>"
<%- end -%></p>

<p>They have been notified that reservation confirmation is required.</p>

<p>Please confirm or decline their reservation by logging into the site. Just click the link below:</p>

<p><%= @url %></p>

<%= render "/shared/mailers/footer" %>
